# Macro v1.0.0

Macro is a plugin for gedit 3.18+.

This plugin provides a way to record actions and play multiple times, through the Tools > Macro menu.

The Playback action can be executed through Ctrl + Shift + P

# Installation

[Download](https://github.com/DjouGoulart/gedit-macro/releases/latest/) and extract all files to `~/.local/share/gedit/plugins/`.

To turn it on, open gedit, go to Preferences > Plugins and check Macro.

